	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />How mmc3 loads the prg-rom in cpu mem at start?
<br />i read that bank 0 and 1 goes to 0x8000 and 0xC000 (on reset), but if we are talking about 8kb banks it leaves the reset vector empty (0).
<br />
<br />I tried to load as a mmc1 and some games work "d dragon 2", "bart vs the world", but other not.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

