	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />PRG banks $C000 and $E000 are hardwired to the last two banks in the cart (though $C000 can be swapped with $8000, and any game that uses DMC will do this). Banks $8000 and $A000 are potentially unpredictable on startup.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
